  ],
  cadenceData: [],
  csv_names: []
};

export default function (state = initialState, action) {
  switch (action.type) {
    case "GET_INVENTORY_INFO":
      return {
        ...state,
        inventoryInfoData: action.payload,
      };
    case "GET_CADENCE_DATA":
      return {
        ...state,
        cadenceData: action.payload,
          csv_names: action.csv_names,
          skus: action.skus,
          savedData: action.savedData
      };
    default:
      return {
        ...state,
      };
  }
}
